My MSc research focused on understanding sediment dynamics in the Marsyangdi River Basin and how peaking run-of-river hydropower plants alter natural sediment transport processes. The work combined field sampling, GIS analysis, and hydrological modelling to quantify sediment fluxes and assess downstream ecological and infrastructural impacts.
